<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>First fragment</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">la</hi>viṇa nārāyaṇanallata <hi rend="grantha">lā</hi>ṭarāyarāku <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>varāṉa tunaka<hi rend="grantha">ṇḍi naragiri</hi>nāyakkar <hi rend="grantha">pautra</hi>rar <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>tunaka<hi rend="grantha">ṇḍi</hi> ciṅkama nāyakkar Upaiya<hi rend="grantha">m rātri</hi>tiruvā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>taḷikai Oṉṟukku Amutupaṭi paruppamutu <unclear>miḷa</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>paṭṭavakai ku <hi rend="grantha">śrīse</hi>nāpatipperu<unclear>vilai</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ḻaṉāṭu melaimuṟi perumāḷ ciraṅka <unclear>rācarti</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>ku<unclear>ṭi</unclear> rācavipāṭaṉāl rūpāy 2- li Innila <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>Second fragment</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Inta poṉ <unclear>nā</unclear>ṉūṟṟu
<lb n="2"/>Irupatukku muṭalāka nila
<lb n="3" break="no"/>m Iruveliyum <hi rend="grantha">śrīse</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nāpatip peruvilaiyāka
<lb n="5"/>vi<unclear>lai</unclear> <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>paṇṭārattile
<lb n="6"/>Inta po<supplied reason="omitted">ṉ</supplied> nānūṟṟirupa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tum celuttikkoṇ
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>ṭa paṭiyāle</unclear> Inta
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>Another disconnected fragment near this in slightly larger characters reads:</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Ālaṅkuṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>pa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṭi tevar <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ka <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>tu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kuṭinallūr
</p>

